com.launchdarkly.android.flagstore

Interface FlagStoreManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SharedPrefsFlagStoreManager
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface FlagStoreManager
    A FlagStoreManager is responsible for managing FlagStores for active and recently active users, as well as providing flagKey specific update callbacks.

        void switchToUser(java.lang.String userKey)
        Deprecated. 
        Loads the FlagStore for the particular userKey. If too many users have a locally cached FlagStore, deletes the oldest.
        Parameters:
        userKey - The key representing the user to switch to
